    "Our generator constructs these tasks from the ground up, selecting appropriate atom tasks based on room attributes, required materials, and agent information, and then automatically scales them into full-fledged puzzles.",
    "The generator also ensures task feasibility by ac- counting for agent cooperation and item dependencies.",
    "For consistent LLM testing, we've designated seeds for each of the five difficulty levels, with 25 unique tasks in total, and set a default simultaneous item activation wait time of 30 seconds for task completion.",
    "Benchmarking Our VillagerAgent in Overcooked-AI.",
    "We conducted tests on VillagerAgent (equipped with GPT-4) within the Overcooked environment, following the methodology used in ProAgent (Zhang et al., 2024)."
